--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CHANGES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        o
    ____|____
   |         |  This file lists changes made to the Ansible role.
   |  _   _  |  The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and
   | [_] [_] |  formatted to allow easy grepping by scripts.
   |____~____|
    ___//__//   The fields are:
   /|     |/    B: bug
  //|_____|     F: feature
    _|| ||_     I: improvement
   (__| |__)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.8.0 (2016-04-09)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.2-RELEASE

* Version 0.7.0 (2016-04-02)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 5.9
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 5.8

* Version 0.6.0 (2016-02-28)
F: Add support for OS family 'OpenBSD'

* Version 0.5.0 (2016-01-21)
F: Drop support for OS family 'Gentoo'

* Version 0.4.5 (2015-11-17)
I: Add missing Ansible tags

* Version 0.4.4 (2015-11-08)
I: Improve 'group_vars' and 'host_vars' options

* Version 0.4.3 (2015-04-10)
B: Fix 'group_state' option

* Version 0.4.2 (2014-12-23)
I: Various small Ansible and Jinja2 improvements

* Version 0.4.1 (2014-09-11)
I: Change license from 'GPLv2' to 'Simplified BSD License'

* Version 0.4.0 (2014-08-28)
F: Add support for OS family 'FreeBSD'

* Version 0.3.0 (2014-08-14)
F: Remove support for OS family 'RedHat'

* Version 0.2.0 (2014-07-17)
F: Add support for 'default' and 'custom' group

* Version 0.1.2 (2014-07-06)
I: Improve conditional checks

* Version 0.1.1 (2014-06-26)
B: Add missing bracket at end of when statement

* Version 0.1.0 (2014-05-03)
F: Initial release
